title: Enjoying Physical Intimacy as a Woman, Part 5
itunes:author: Guests: Dr. Cliff & Joyce Penner
itunes:summary: Making time for romance and sexual intimacy are great gifts for your marriage. While it's not always convenient during busy seasons, we should not neglect them. Greg and John explain why sex is important and beneficial for your marriage. Receive the book Enjoy! with your gift of any amount!
